For mac users:
  Open terminal and follow the steps.
    On OS X, install PortAudio using Homebrew: brew install portaudio.  
    Then, install PyAudio using Pip: pip3 install pyaudio.
    Install Urllib to run threads by using: pip install urllib3
    Then you have to install SpeechRecognition using: pip3 install SpeechRecognition.
    Since I am using an google API install: pip3 install google-api-python-client
  
  For Google search:
    Install library by: pip3 install google.
 
*Note: pip3 for python3.
